# Title: Okta 2023 Breach Indicator Of Compromise
# Author: Muhammad Faisal (@faisalusuf)
# Date: 2023-10-25
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects new user account creation or activation with specific names related to the Okta Support System 2023 breach.
# This rule can be enhanced by filtering out known and legitimate username used in your environnement.
# MITRE Tactic: Credential Access
# Tags: attack.credential-access, detection.emerging-threats

eventtype IN ("user.lifecycle.create", "user.lifecycle.activate") target.user.display.name="*svc_network_backup*"